NodeJs weather forecast component

Prerequisites:

1. npm install

2. npm start

3. go to: http://localhost:8081/weatherByCity

4. profit


Project scrapes weather forecasts from ilmatieteenlaitos.fi. User can declare amout of days forecasts shown
from 1 to 10 days, by changing config.json value.

Cities can be changed by adding, or removing strings into "city" array in server.js

If temperature drops below 0-celcius, it changes the status value from "Ok" = "DANGER".

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Other:

Component is controlled with callbacks over promise, because "Request" -module needs extra module to work with
promises.